  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Access </strong>zebra</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Range </strong>30 feet; <strong>Targets </strong>1 animal companion</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Duration </strong>10 minutes</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You bring out the rarest traits of an animal companion, those only known in the most obscure texts. Make a Nature check against the standard DC of the animal companion's level. On a success, it is granted 1 familiar point. On a critical success it is granted 2. These points are immediately spent as you please, granting the animal companion familiar abilities. You may not select master abilities.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened </strong>(+1) The duration of the spell extends by 1 hour.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened </strong>(+1) Allow Arcane, Religion, or Occultism to be used instead of Nature</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened </strong>(+3) The duration of the spell becomes 1 day.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Heightened (+3) Target another animal companion within range. All targets gain the same familiar traits.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>"
